name: NewMovies
0:

”Alexa, start New Movies”
”Alexa, ask New Movies what's new”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: new movies
des: This skill retrieves the latest movie releases from the Movie Database (www.themoviedb.org) and tells you them in order of popularity
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
